Titolo: Robot Odyssey

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Robot Odyssey was an adventure game published by The Learning Company in 1984 and released for the Apple II, TRS-80 Color Computer, and DOS. Most players have found it incredibly challenging. The player is readying for bed when, suddenly, they fall through the floor into an underground city of robots, Robotropolis. The player begins in the sewers of the city with three programmable robots, and must make their way to the top of the city to try to find their way home again.

Genere: Puzzle video game

Valutazione: N/A
